1
00:00:00,630 --> 00:00:03,209
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,339 --> 00:00:06,099
<Default><b>[FEMALE STUDENT 06-A]
Bye!</b></Default>

3
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:09,330
<Default><b>- Ren!
- Hm?</b></Default>

4
00:00:09,929 --> 00:00:11,776
<Default><b>[FEMALE STUDENT 06-B]
Brave Star at your place again?</b></Default>

5
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:13,849
<Default><b>[chuckles]
Sure I'm down.</b></Default>

6
00:00:13,970 --> 00:00:16,230
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Everyone wants to come!</b></Default>

7
00:00:16,350 --> 00:00:17,826
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- You gotta show them</b></Default>

8
00:00:17,850 --> 00:00:19,530
<Default><b>how good you are at it!</b></Default>

9
00:00:19,649 --> 00:00:20,835
<Default><b>Sorry, but I'm busy.</b></Default>

10
00:00:20,859 --> 00:00:21,956
<Default><b>[FEMALE STUDENT 06-B]
What?</b></Default>

11
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:24,335
<Default><b>That's not what you
were about to say earlier!</b></Default>

12
00:00:24,359 --> 00:00:25,875
<Default><b>Can't believe you're friends
with that guy.</b></Default>

13
00:00:25,899 --> 00:00:27,046
<Default><b>[MALE STUDENT 06-B]
Yeah, I've never even</b></Default>

14
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:28,470
<Default><b>heard him speak.</b></Default>

15
00:00:29,070 --> 00:00:30,910
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

16
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:40,789
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

17
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,500
<Default><b>- [explosion]
- Huh?</b></Default>

18
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:49,606
<Default><b>Did you finish
off the others?</b></Default>

19
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:52,390
<Default><b>[grunts] Yeah.
We just barely managed it.</b></Default>

20
00:00:52,969 --> 00:00:54,849
<Default><b>Wow you're
amazing, Sir Ren!</b></Default>

21
00:00:55,009 --> 00:00:57,405
<Default><b>You took down this dragon
all by yourself?</b></Default>

22
00:00:57,429 --> 00:00:59,669
<Default><b>The dragon's weak spot
is its stomach.</b></Default>

23
00:00:59,729 --> 00:01:02,286
<Default><b>Focus all your attacks there
and it's laughable.</b></Default>

24
00:01:02,310 --> 00:01:03,746
<Default><b>[PARTY MEMBER 06-A (M)]
Sir Ren knows everything</b></Default>

25
00:01:03,770 --> 00:01:05,126
<Default><b>- doesn't he?
- That's why he's a hero!</b></Default>

26
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:07,830
<Default><b>[REN] I knew this world
like the back of my hand.</b></Default>

27
00:01:08,489 --> 00:01:11,030
<Default><b>Because it was exactly
the same as the VRMMO</b></Default>

28
00:01:11,109 --> 00:01:13,429
<Default><b>I used to play
called Brave Star Online.</b></Default>

29
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,159
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

30
00:01:16,870 --> 00:01:18,305
<Default><b>[REN]
Okay, let's go!</b></Default>

31
00:01:18,329 --> 00:01:19,476
<Default><b>But it's huge!</b></Default>

32
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,500
<Default><b>Can we beat
something that big?</b></Default>

33
00:01:21,709 --> 00:01:24,129
<Default><b>Yes. I doubt this will be
any trouble.</b></Default>

34
00:01:25,379 --> 00:01:26,539
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

35
00:01:26,709 --> 00:01:28,066
<Default><b>[REN] At the time</b></Default>

36
00:01:28,090 --> 00:01:30,570
<Default><b>I felt strong enough
to speed run the world.</b></Default>

37
00:01:31,129 --> 00:01:32,729
<Default><b>I really believed it.</b></Default>

38
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:36,199
<Default><b>Until that moment.</b></Default>

39
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:18,120
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

40
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:21,080
<Default><b>[REN]
Why? Why couldn't I win?</b></Default>

41
00:03:22,409 --> 00:03:24,689
<Default><b>I followed
the online guides perfectly.</b></Default>

42
00:03:25,370 --> 00:03:27,850
<Default><b>They said it should be
beatable at level 60.</b></Default>

43
00:03:28,789 --> 00:03:30,869
<Default><b>And all of us
were above level 80!</b></Default>

44
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:32,250
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

45
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,710
<Default><b>[shrieks]</b></Default>

46
00:03:34,129 --> 00:03:36,259
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

47
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,950
<Default><b>This is impossible.</b></Default>

48
00:03:40,139 --> 00:03:42,699
<Default><b>Level 80 should've been
more than high enough.</b></Default>

49
00:03:42,889 --> 00:03:44,609
<Default><b>My companions were weak.</b></Default>

50
00:03:45,020 --> 00:03:46,455
<Default><b>That's why we lost!</b></Default>

51
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:48,665
<Default><b>It's not my fault!
It's not my fault!</b></Default>

52
00:03:48,689 --> 00:03:50,165
<Default><b>It's not my fault!</b></Default>

53
00:03:50,189 --> 00:03:52,569
<Default><b>[thumps]
It's not my fault!</b></Default>

54
00:03:52,819 --> 00:03:55,439
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] [grunts]
Ren, I'm sorry</b></Default>

55
00:03:55,530 --> 00:03:57,256
<Default><b>you had to
go through that</b></Default>

56
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,600
<Default><b>but it doesn't mean
you have to give up.</b></Default>

57
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:02,660
<Default><b>It's only a matter of time
before the Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

58
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:06,120
<Default><b>When it does, we heroes need
to fight against it together.</b></Default>

59
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:08,140
<Default><b>Please, fight with me.</b></Default>

60
00:04:09,169 --> 00:04:10,849
<Default><b>[REN] All right.
[thump]</b></Default>

61
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,855
<Default><b>[MYNE] How dare you put
your trust in the Shield Demon!</b></Default>

62
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:17,009
<Default><b>[REN] To be honest, I didn't
believe her either at first.</b></Default>

63
00:04:17,629 --> 00:04:20,050
<Default><b>But, her tears
were real.</b></Default>

64
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,040
<Default><b>Not to mention.</b></Default>

65
00:04:22,889 --> 00:04:24,289
<Default><b>Her slave crest.</b></Default>

66
00:04:25,810 --> 00:04:26,850
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

67
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,940
<Default><b>I care about you more than
anyone in this world, Ren!</b></Default>

68
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,875
<Default><b>Everyone else may think you
to be a criminal</b></Default>

69
00:04:33,899 --> 00:04:36,339
<Default><b>but I know with all my heart
you're a hero.</b></Default>

70
00:04:38,029 --> 00:04:39,086
<Default><b>I believe you fought</b></Default>

71
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:41,430
<Default><b>for the sake of the world
that day, Ren.</b></Default>

72
00:04:42,829 --> 00:04:45,740
<Default><b>[REN] That's right.
I didn't do anything wrong!</b></Default>

73
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,620
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

74
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,266
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
If that's how you're gonna be</b></Default>

75
00:04:51,290 --> 00:04:53,530
<Default><b>I've got some shit
to say to you, too.</b></Default>

76
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:57,219
<Default><b>This world isn't
some game.</b></Default>

77
00:04:57,339 --> 00:04:59,605
<Default><b>You had loyal followers
who believed in you.</b></Default>

78
00:04:59,629 --> 00:05:01,069
<Default><b>Shut the hell up!</b></Default>

79
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,946
<Default><b>[REN] From now on</b></Default>

80
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:04,865
<Default><b>everything's going
to be just fine!</b></Default>

81
00:05:04,889 --> 00:05:06,809
<Default><b>I was just
unlucky until now!</b></Default>

82
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:08,330
<Default><b>It's not my fault.</b></Default>

83
00:05:09,810 --> 00:05:11,245
<Default><b>And unlike the others</b></Default>

84
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:13,629
<Default><b>she's a true comrade
that's worthy of me.</b></Default>

85
00:05:13,899 --> 00:05:15,730
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

86
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:20,199
<Default><b>[rain splattering]</b></Default>

87
00:05:21,949 --> 00:05:23,069
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

88
00:05:27,699 --> 00:05:29,209
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

89
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,280
<Default><b>Where'd all my equipment go?
[gasps]</b></Default>

90
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,400
<Default><b>- [thuds]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

91
00:05:36,089 --> 00:05:37,089
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

92
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:42,355
<Default><b>[MYNE] Seeing as you're useless
to me now</b></Default>

93
00:05:42,379 --> 00:05:43,615
<Default><b>I figured I'd go
ahead and take</b></Default>

94
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,576
<Default><b>what useful things
you had left.</b></Default>

95
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,760
<Default><b>[REN] Huh!</b></Default>

96
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,680
<Default><b>No way.</b></Default>

97
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:51,100
<Default><b>Me? Useless?</b></Default>

98
00:05:51,939 --> 00:05:53,060
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

99
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:56,269
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

100
00:06:07,949 --> 00:06:08,989
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

101
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:11,500
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

102
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,870
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

103
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:21,696
<Default><b>[laughs]
Well, would ya look at that.</b></Default>

104
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,776
<Default><b>It's the Sword Hero.</b></Default>

105
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,120
<Default><b>Here, just like
that woman said he'd be.</b></Default>

106
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:26,550
<Default><b>[Ren gasps]</b></Default>

107
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:27,720
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

108
00:06:32,139 --> 00:06:33,499
<Default><b>[grunts] Again.</b></Default>

109
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,230
<Default><b>[laughs] Too slow!</b></Default>

110
00:06:37,939 --> 00:06:40,939
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

111
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:43,716
<Default><b>[REN] What's going on?
Why are they after me?</b></Default>

112
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:46,490
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

113
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:49,620
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

114
00:06:50,829 --> 00:06:52,389
<Default><b>- [door creaks]
- Hm.</b></Default>

115
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,846
<Default><b>Mommy, help!</b></Default>

116
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:56,670
<Default><b>- A bad guy got in the house!
- No wait, I'm a hero!</b></Default>

117
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,550
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [child crying]</b></Default>

118
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:02,199
<Default><b>- [MOTHER 06-A] The Sword Hero?
- Huh?</b></Default>

119
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:05,220
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

120
00:07:05,509 --> 00:07:08,100
<Default><b>That's right. Forgive me.
I'm being chased.</b></Default>

121
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,446
<Default><b>So it's dangerous
out there.</b></Default>

122
00:07:10,470 --> 00:07:11,576
<Default><b>Stay inside
and you'll be safe...</b></Default>

123
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,160
<Default><b>Get out of my house.</b></Default>

124
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:15,230
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

125
00:07:16,019 --> 00:07:17,956
<Default><b>We counted on you
to protect our village</b></Default>

126
00:07:17,980 --> 00:07:19,375
<Default><b>from the
Spirit Tortoise.</b></Default>

127
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:21,545
<Default><b>How dare you show
your face around here!</b></Default>

128
00:07:21,569 --> 00:07:23,149
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

129
00:07:24,069 --> 00:07:25,505
<Default><b>Get out of here
before you bring</b></Default>

130
00:07:25,529 --> 00:07:27,529
<Default><b>another disaster
to our village!</b></Default>

131
00:07:28,699 --> 00:07:29,739
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

132
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:31,860
<Default><b>[door slams]</b></Default>

133
00:07:32,579 --> 00:07:34,790
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

134
00:07:38,209 --> 00:07:39,750
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

135
00:07:40,089 --> 00:07:41,729
<Default><b>[MAN 05-B]
There he is!</b></Default>

136
00:07:42,129 --> 00:07:43,209
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

137
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:46,300
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

138
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:01,270
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

139
00:08:01,689 --> 00:08:02,939
<Default><b>[coughing]</b></Default>

140
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:10,120
<Default><b>[grunts]
I'm... I'm a hero, dammit!</b></Default>

141
00:08:11,329 --> 00:08:12,886
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-A]
Well, well, well</b></Default>

142
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:15,290
<Default><b>if it isn't the all mighty
Sword Hero.</b></Default>

143
00:08:15,699 --> 00:08:17,846
<Default><b>What are you doing
out here all alone, huh?</b></Default>

144
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,846
<Default><b>Where are your
other party members?</b></Default>

145
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:22,000
<Default><b>Oh, I remember now</b></Default>

146
00:08:22,089 --> 00:08:24,209
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

147
00:08:24,709 --> 00:08:26,646
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-D] What happened
to your clothes, Sword Hero?</b></Default>

148
00:08:26,670 --> 00:08:27,735
<Default><b>They're covered in mud!</b></Default>

149
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:29,565
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-B] Maybe he's not
the Sword Hero then.</b></Default>

150
00:08:29,589 --> 00:08:32,269
<Default><b>- He's the Mud Hero!
- How did this happen to me?</b></Default>

151
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:34,590
<Default><b>[REN] These losers
are laughing at me.</b></Default>

152
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:38,060
<Default><b>And that woman took every piece
of gear that I owned.</b></Default>

153
00:08:38,809 --> 00:08:42,480
<Default><b>I don't need companions.
I can get by fine by myself.</b></Default>

154
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:45,820
<Default><b>After all, I know everything
about this world!</b></Default>

155
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,360
<Default><b>I was chosen
to be a hero!</b></Default>

156
00:08:48,990 --> 00:08:52,570
<Default><b>[grunts] This wasn't how it was
supposed to be, dammit!</b></Default>

157
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,950
<Default><b>[bandits gasp]</b></Default>

158
00:08:55,029 --> 00:08:57,700
<Default><b>[whooshing]</b></Default>

159
00:09:00,289 --> 00:09:02,129
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

160
00:09:07,379 --> 00:09:08,859
<Default><b>I'll kill you all.</b></Default>

161
00:09:10,049 --> 00:09:11,529
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

162
00:09:16,179 --> 00:09:17,365
<Default><b>[bandit 06-B screams]</b></Default>

163
00:09:17,389 --> 00:09:19,495
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-C] Wait! Stop!
Please don't hurt us!</b></Default>

164
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:21,375
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-D] Boss, quick!
What do we do?</b></Default>

165
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:23,456
<Default><b>[BANDIT 06-A] Don't just
stand there, go kill him!</b></Default>

166
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,399
<Default><b>[bandits screaming]</b></Default>

167
00:09:27,070 --> 00:09:28,110
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

168
00:09:28,779 --> 00:09:31,779
<Default><b>[bandits whimpering]</b></Default>

169
00:09:43,129 --> 00:09:45,789
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

170
00:09:49,509 --> 00:09:51,179
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

171
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:56,389
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

172
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:58,470
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

173
00:09:59,970 --> 00:10:01,130
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

174
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:03,309
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

175
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,760
<Default><b>Out of my way.</b></Default>

176
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,300
<Default><b>Prepare yourself!</b></Default>

177
00:10:14,529 --> 00:10:16,830
<Default><b>- [both grunt]
- [laughs]</b></Default>

178
00:10:17,539 --> 00:10:19,135
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] Ren?
- Huh?</b></Default>

179
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,199
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

180
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:22,290
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Oh! Greetings, father!</b></Default>

181
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,340
<Default><b>Motoyasu?
What are you doing here?</b></Default>

182
00:10:26,629 --> 00:10:27,765
<Default><b>Defeating these bandits</b></Default>

183
00:10:27,789 --> 00:10:29,485
<Default><b>before they attack
your village!</b></Default>

184
00:10:29,509 --> 00:10:31,909
<Default><b>Think of all trouble
they would cause you!</b></Default>

185
00:10:32,509 --> 00:10:35,179
<Default><b>I figured I'd start
by luring out their leader.</b></Default>

186
00:10:35,389 --> 00:10:37,076
<Default><b>Only to find
that their leader</b></Default>

187
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:39,759
<Default><b>is someone that we know</b></Default>

188
00:10:42,309 --> 00:10:43,769
<Default><b>Ren, are you?</b></Default>

189
00:10:46,019 --> 00:10:48,110
<Default><b>Maneater. Meteor Slash!</b></Default>

190
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:49,940
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

191
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:53,070
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

192
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:55,370
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I know this feeling.</b></Default>

193
00:10:56,779 --> 00:10:58,579
<Default><b>- [sword clangs]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

194
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:03,599
<Default><b>The Curse Series?</b></Default>

195
00:11:05,250 --> 00:11:06,330
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

196
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:08,780
<Default><b>[exhales]
You think I'm a failure too</b></Default>

197
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,360
<Default><b>don't you, Naofumi?</b></Default>

198
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,280
<Default><b>I'm going to be stronger
than everyone.</b></Default>

199
00:11:14,009 --> 00:11:15,025
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

200
00:11:15,049 --> 00:11:17,529
<Default><b>There's no one left
to hold me back anymore.</b></Default>

201
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:20,509
<Default><b>I'm going to awaken
an even greater power here</b></Default>

202
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,245
<Default><b>and defeat both of you!</b></Default>

203
00:11:22,269 --> 00:11:24,929
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

204
00:11:25,269 --> 00:11:27,269
<Default><b>- [sighs]
- [sword clanging]</b></Default>

205
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,400
<Default><b>I'll awaken
all of my abilities</b></Default>

206
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:32,899
<Default><b>defeat every enemy</b></Default>

207
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:35,210
<Default><b>Master every power!</b></Default>

208
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:38,040
<Default><b>And become the strongest
in every world that exists!</b></Default>

209
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,216
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] He's reduced himself
to a bandit.</b></Default>

210
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,306
<Default><b>But his greed's
driving him</b></Default>

211
00:11:41,330 --> 00:11:43,330
<Default><b>to seek more
than just treasure.</b></Default>

212
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:46,710
<Default><b>What he wants is victory.
What he craves is power.</b></Default>

213
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,629
<Default><b>This curse is... greed!</b></Default>

214
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:52,726
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [NAOFUMI] But I don't get it.</b></Default>

215
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:54,936
<Default><b>Why does he still feel
so weak and pathetic?</b></Default>

216
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,880
<Default><b>Stop looking
at me like that!</b></Default>

217
00:11:57,299 --> 00:11:58,566
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Whatever the reason</b></Default>

218
00:11:58,590 --> 00:12:00,826
<Default><b>the Curse Series has skills
that make you pay a price</b></Default>

219
00:12:00,850 --> 00:12:02,530
<Default><b>each time you use them.</b></Default>

220
00:12:02,809 --> 00:12:04,329
<Default><b>I need to stop him!</b></Default>

221
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:07,440
<Default><b>You'll never defeat me</b></Default>

222
00:12:07,769 --> 00:12:09,076
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I got a question!</b></Default>

223
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,785
<Default><b>Why isn't your comrade witch
with you?</b></Default>

224
00:12:10,809 --> 00:12:11,849
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

225
00:12:11,899 --> 00:12:14,690
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

226
00:12:19,860 --> 00:12:22,700
<Default><b>Careful, father!
You're only making him angrier!</b></Default>

227
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,635
<Default><b>Ren, I swear
I'm not your enemy!</b></Default>

228
00:12:25,659 --> 00:12:26,846
<Default><b>- Shut the hell up!
- Oo! Oo!</b></Default>

229
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,590
<Default><b>Don't forget that I'm here
if you need me, father!</b></Default>

230
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:31,395
<Default><b>Shall I kill
him for you?</b></Default>

231
00:12:31,419 --> 00:12:32,936
<Default><b>No, just let
me handle him!</b></Default>

232
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,525
<Default><b>Ren, you gotta
calm down!</b></Default>

233
00:12:34,549 --> 00:12:35,379
<Default><b>Being a bandit leader</b></Default>

234
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:36,735
<Default><b>isn't going to help you
get back what you...</b></Default>

235
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:38,719
<Default><b>I call upon thy
twisted power.</b></Default>

236
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:41,000
<Default><b>Let this sinner
pay for his misdeeds</b></Default>

237
00:12:41,049 --> 00:12:42,826
<Default><b>with an execution
by beheading.</b></Default>

238
00:12:42,850 --> 00:12:43,890
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

239
00:12:45,009 --> 00:12:46,969
<Default><b>[REN]
Let him writhe in despair</b></Default>

240
00:12:47,309 --> 00:12:49,589
<Default><b>as his head is separated
from his body.</b></Default>

241
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:53,140
<Default><b>- Guillotine.
- [chains rattling]</b></Default>

242
00:12:53,399 --> 00:12:56,399
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

243
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:05,120
<Default><b>I've had enough
of this shit!</b></Default>

244
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,450
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

245
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,550
<Default><b>- [Naofumi grunts]
- Ha!</b></Default>

246
00:13:09,210 --> 00:13:10,490
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

247
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:14,340
<Default><b>Keep your
distance from him!</b></Default>

248
00:13:15,169 --> 00:13:16,969
<Default><b>I'll be fine,
don't worry!</b></Default>

249
00:13:18,129 --> 00:13:20,089
<Default><b>All of these
teams and guilds.</b></Default>

250
00:13:20,129 --> 00:13:23,209
<Default><b>You're all worthless when it
comes to fighting on your own!</b></Default>

251
00:13:23,929 --> 00:13:25,405
<Default><b>Let this foolish sinner</b></Default>

252
00:13:25,429 --> 00:13:28,149
<Default><b>standing here before me
pay for his transgressions</b></Default>

253
00:13:28,220 --> 00:13:30,820
<Default><b>by being crushed to death
in the name of a God!</b></Default>

254
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:33,649
<Default><b>Take my riches
and deliver a divine strike</b></Default>

255
00:13:33,730 --> 00:13:36,360
<Default><b>that will purge my enemies
from this world!</b></Default>

256
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,240
<Default><b>Witness Gold Rebellion!</b></Default>

257
00:13:41,610 --> 00:13:43,210
<Default><b>- [growling]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

258
00:13:48,659 --> 00:13:50,059
<Default><b>[Naofumi grunts]</b></Default>

259
00:13:50,659 --> 00:13:54,169
<Default><b>[groaning] Hold him off
for me, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

260
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:55,726
<Default><b>[REN] Damn it!
I'm not done yet!</b></Default>

261
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,226
<Default><b>I can still
get stronger!</b></Default>

262
00:13:57,250 --> 00:14:00,210
<Default><b>I'm stronger alone than
any number of these cowards</b></Default>

263
00:14:00,299 --> 00:14:02,699
<Default><b>who need to gang up
on me in order to win!</b></Default>

264
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:05,220
<Default><b>I'll show you how limitless
my strength is!</b></Default>

265
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,446
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

266
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:07,720
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

267
00:14:09,019 --> 00:14:10,019
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

268
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,809
<Default><b>Hey, S'yne</b></Default>

269
00:14:12,889 --> 00:14:15,409
<Default><b>so the curse doesn't consume
any more of him.</b></Default>

270
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,916
<Default><b>After that, we
can restrain him</b></Default>

271
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:18,755
<Default><b>and take him back
to the village with us.</b></Default>

272
00:14:18,779 --> 00:14:20,779
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
Pardon me, Sir Naofumi.</b></Default>

273
00:14:21,490 --> 00:14:23,255
<Default><b>But if you'd permit me
to do so</b></Default>

274
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:25,505
<Default><b>I'd like to duel
the Sword Hero alone.</b></Default>

275
00:14:25,529 --> 00:14:26,806
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Are you serious?</b></Default>

276
00:14:26,830 --> 00:14:27,830
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

277
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:31,500
<Default><b>I am. I can bring him
back to his senses.</b></Default>

278
00:14:32,789 --> 00:14:33,869
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

279
00:14:34,289 --> 00:14:35,806
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Now that I think about it</b></Default>

280
00:14:35,830 --> 00:14:38,390
<Default><b>Eclair is far better
with a sword than Ren is.</b></Default>

281
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,150
<Default><b>She can win this.</b></Default>

282
00:14:41,009 --> 00:14:42,355
<Default><b>He has more
buffs as a hero</b></Default>

283
00:14:42,379 --> 00:14:44,459
<Default><b>so I'll cast
support magic on you.</b></Default>

284
00:14:44,509 --> 00:14:46,485
<Default><b>My only condition
is I get to intervene</b></Default>

285
00:14:46,509 --> 00:14:47,865
<Default><b>if things start
to look bad.</b></Default>

286
00:14:47,889 --> 00:14:51,059
<Default><b>- Is that all right with you?
- Yes. Thank you.</b></Default>

287
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:53,290
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

288
00:14:54,649 --> 00:14:57,480
<Default><b>- [shuddered breathing]
- [ECLAIR] Sword Hero</b></Default>

289
00:14:57,559 --> 00:14:59,730
<Default><b>- I challenge you to a duel.
- Hm.</b></Default>

290
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,940
<Default><b>My name is
Eclair Seaetto.</b></Default>

291
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:06,370
<Default><b>And if you wish to fight
the Shield and Spear Heroes</b></Default>

292
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:08,090
<Default><b>you must defeat me!</b></Default>

293
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:11,580
<Default><b>I don't care who you are.
You'll fall like all the rest!</b></Default>

294
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:16,120
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

295
00:15:20,129 --> 00:15:21,145
<Default><b>I dunno about this</b></Default>

296
00:15:21,169 --> 00:15:23,235
<Default><b>can she really take him
in a one-on-one duel?</b></Default>

297
00:15:23,259 --> 00:15:24,735
<Default><b>She's strong,
but he's a hero!</b></Default>

298
00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:26,196
<Default><b>She'll be just fine.</b></Default>

299
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:28,540
<Default><b>This is Eclair
that we're talking about!</b></Default>

300
00:15:30,049 --> 00:15:32,100
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

301
00:15:32,809 --> 00:15:34,666
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] In a way I think
I might understand</b></Default>

302
00:15:34,690 --> 00:15:36,530
<Default><b>how Eclair
feels right now.</b></Default>

303
00:15:37,860 --> 00:15:40,980
<Default><b>When he swings his sword</b></Default>

304
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:43,460
<Default><b>Tell me Sword Hero</b></Default>

305
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:45,926
<Default><b>what do you seek
to gain from all this?</b></Default>

306
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:48,110
<Default><b>And why do you wish
to get stronger?</b></Default>

307
00:15:48,409 --> 00:15:51,450
<Default><b>I refuse to accept anything
less than being the strongest!</b></Default>

308
00:15:52,490 --> 00:15:55,080
<Default><b>Strongest in the world</b></Default>

309
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,520
<Default><b>the strongest
out of all the dimensions!</b></Default>

310
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:59,816
<Default><b>- That's why I have...
- [ECLAIR] And then what?</b></Default>

311
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,840
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

312
00:16:03,299 --> 00:16:05,316
<Default><b>Once you have become
the strongest</b></Default>

313
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,980
<Default><b>what will you do then?</b></Default>

314
00:16:09,889 --> 00:16:12,639
<Default><b>After I become
the strongest</b></Default>

315
00:16:12,929 --> 00:16:14,639
<Default><b>I, I'm going to...</b></Default>

316
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,080
<Default><b>To save the world!</b></Default>

317
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:21,416
<Default><b>That's right!
I'm the chosen hero!</b></Default>

318
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:23,755
<Default><b>The Sword Hero that's
going to save this world</b></Default>

319
00:16:23,779 --> 00:16:25,059
<Default><b>from despair!</b></Default>

320
00:16:25,899 --> 00:16:27,490
<Default><b>Now die!</b></Default>

321
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:29,505
<Default><b>- [sword clanging]
- [Ren gasps]</b></Default>

322
00:16:29,529 --> 00:16:32,249
<Default><b>That was a task that
someone else thrust upon you!</b></Default>

323
00:16:32,830 --> 00:16:34,910
<Default><b>I'm asking
what you yourself want!</b></Default>

324
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,040
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

325
00:16:40,710 --> 00:16:42,670
<Default><b>Decide what you wish
to aim for</b></Default>

326
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:44,919
<Default><b>then fully commit
to your attack.</b></Default>

327
00:16:50,049 --> 00:16:51,655
<Default><b>It's obvious that
you're not committing</b></Default>

328
00:16:51,679 --> 00:16:53,235
<Default><b>to anything right now.</b></Default>

329
00:16:53,259 --> 00:16:55,076
<Default><b>And you cannot defeat me
with your heart</b></Default>

330
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,929
<Default><b>in such a
state, can you?</b></Default>

331
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,350
<Default><b>You shut up.</b></Default>

332
00:17:00,139 --> 00:17:01,480
<Default><b>Shut up!</b></Default>

333
00:17:03,899 --> 00:17:07,150
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

334
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:08,359
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

335
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:12,660
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]
I am the strongest.</b></Default>

336
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:16,410
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

337
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,920
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

338
00:17:28,549 --> 00:17:31,259
<Default><b>To gain the strength
to be the strongest.</b></Default>

339
00:17:31,970 --> 00:17:33,849
<Default><b>To gain everything.</b></Default>

340
00:17:34,509 --> 00:17:38,309
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

341
00:17:38,430 --> 00:17:39,849
<Default><b>[burbling]</b></Default>

342
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:44,819
<Default><b>Devour all.</b></Default>

343
00:17:45,859 --> 00:17:46,979
<Default><b>"Devour."</b></Default>

344
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,005
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
My curse is wrath.</b></Default>

345
00:17:49,029 --> 00:17:52,490
<Default><b>So Ren has two.
Greed and gluttony?</b></Default>

346
00:17:53,029 --> 00:17:55,069
<Default><b>It's like
the seven deadly sins!</b></Default>

347
00:17:57,119 --> 00:17:59,359
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
You're suffering, aren't you?</b></Default>

348
00:18:01,079 --> 00:18:03,539
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

349
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:07,420
<Default><b>I'll put an end
to your pain.</b></Default>

350
00:18:14,009 --> 00:18:15,849
<Default><b>Hengen Muso Swordcraft</b></Default>

351
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:17,485
<Default><b>Multistrike Crumble!</b></Default>

352
00:18:17,509 --> 00:18:19,930
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

353
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,650
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

354
00:18:31,069 --> 00:18:32,609
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

355
00:18:34,529 --> 00:18:35,529
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

356
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:43,869
<Default><b>[laughing]
There you are, Sword Hero!</b></Default>

357
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,765
<Default><b>[REN]
I've seen those two before.</b></Default>

358
00:18:45,789 --> 00:18:47,630
<Default><b>What the hell</b></Default>

359
00:18:47,710 --> 00:18:49,565
<Default><b>And the Shield Hero's
here, too!</b></Default>

360
00:18:49,589 --> 00:18:52,189
<Default><b>We're gonna make you regret
killing us earlier!</b></Default>

361
00:18:52,299 --> 00:18:54,539
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Damn, why now, of all times?</b></Default>

362
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:56,946
<Default><b>They're gonna try
to crush us again!</b></Default>

363
00:18:56,970 --> 00:18:59,349
<Default><b>All right! Time to die</b></Default>

364
00:18:59,430 --> 00:19:02,430
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

365
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:03,519
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

366
00:19:03,599 --> 00:19:05,599
<Default><b>- [groans]
- [gasp]</b></Default>

367
00:19:05,849 --> 00:19:07,269
<Default><b>Eat this, I say!</b></Default>

368
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,819
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

369
00:19:12,109 --> 00:19:14,109
<Default><b>No way! How
is this possible?</b></Default>

370
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:16,240
<Default><b>- [both gasp]
- Motoyasu.</b></Default>

371
00:19:17,319 --> 00:19:19,200
<Default><b>Any last words,
assassin?</b></Default>

372
00:19:19,619 --> 00:19:21,539
<Default><b>- [screams]
- He's fast!</b></Default>

373
00:19:22,329 --> 00:19:23,969
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [slashing]</b></Default>

374
00:19:24,829 --> 00:19:26,710
<Default><b>[blood splatters]</b></Default>

375
00:19:27,289 --> 00:19:28,630
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

376
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,250
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

377
00:19:32,299 --> 00:19:33,299
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

378
00:19:33,759 --> 00:19:34,999
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Huh?</b></Default>

379
00:19:37,589 --> 00:19:38,985
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Ah, I see.</b></Default>

380
00:19:39,009 --> 00:19:40,809
<Default><b>Those must
be their souls!</b></Default>

381
00:19:41,259 --> 00:19:44,019
<Default><b>- Finish 'em.
- Spirit Blade, Soul Slice!</b></Default>

382
00:19:46,230 --> 00:19:48,230
<Default><b>Oh, wow. You
defeated them.</b></Default>

383
00:19:48,730 --> 00:19:49,770
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

384
00:19:50,309 --> 00:19:51,949
<Default><b>He's really something.</b></Default>

385
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:57,410
<Default><b>I'll see to it that all
your enemies lie dead, father.</b></Default>

386
00:19:58,029 --> 00:20:01,119
<Default><b>Motoyasu, where is your
strength coming from exactly?</b></Default>

387
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:04,500
<Default><b>I just followed
your advice</b></Default>

388
00:20:04,579 --> 00:20:05,739
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

389
00:20:05,869 --> 00:20:08,789
<Default><b>You made use of the power-up
methods I told you about?</b></Default>

390
00:20:11,089 --> 00:20:12,569
<Default><b>[REN] He's strong.</b></Default>

391
00:20:17,259 --> 00:20:18,259
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

392
00:20:23,140 --> 00:20:24,866
<Default><b>Why don't we get
stronger together?</b></Default>

393
00:20:24,890 --> 00:20:25,930
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

394
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:31,400
<Default><b>I now know why it is
you were suffering back there.</b></Default>

395
00:20:31,690 --> 00:20:33,956
<Default><b>You didn't want to die
in a place like this</b></Default>

396
00:20:33,980 --> 00:20:35,795
<Default><b>with all the things
you've done.</b></Default>

397
00:20:35,819 --> 00:20:38,490
<Default><b>However, you didn't know
what else to do.</b></Default>

398
00:20:39,359 --> 00:20:41,176
<Default><b>Even if you did manage
to find a way</b></Default>

399
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:43,000
<Default><b>to change and
get stronger</b></Default>

400
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:45,479
<Default><b>the things you've lost
wouldn't come back.</b></Default>

401
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:48,700
<Default><b>And that's exactly why you
should live and keep fighting</b></Default>

402
00:20:48,829 --> 00:20:51,069
<Default><b>to make up for the things
you've lost.</b></Default>

403
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:52,830
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

404
00:20:54,589 --> 00:20:57,109
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] I know that
right now you feel weak.</b></Default>

405
00:20:58,549 --> 00:21:00,349
<Default><b>But I'm sure
within you</b></Default>

406
00:21:02,509 --> 00:21:04,116
<Default><b>lies a sliver
of strength.</b></Default>

407
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,180
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

408
00:21:07,309 --> 00:21:10,940
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

409
00:21:11,099 --> 00:21:12,659
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] Together...</b></Default>

410
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:14,460
<Default><b>We can be stronger!</b></Default>

411
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:17,710
<Default><b>[REN]
This whole time</b></Default>

412
00:21:17,859 --> 00:21:20,099
<Default><b>I thought I'd be
better off on my own.</b></Default>

413
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,805
<Default><b>- [ECLAIR] Hm.
- [Ren gasps]</b></Default>

414
00:21:24,829 --> 00:21:25,910
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

415
00:21:27,450 --> 00:21:30,210
<Default><b>You'll find your reason
to get stronger eventually.</b></Default>

416
00:21:30,869 --> 00:21:32,029
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

417
00:21:32,710 --> 00:21:35,910
<Default><b>And while you're at it, I could
really use a training partner.</b></Default>

418
00:21:37,589 --> 00:21:39,146
<Default><b>- Huh?
- [both chuckle]</b></Default>

419
00:21:39,170 --> 00:21:40,930
<Default><b>You're not hurt</b></Default>

420
00:21:41,009 --> 00:21:42,759
<Default><b>There you are, Filo!</b></Default>

421
00:21:43,390 --> 00:21:46,390
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

422
00:21:47,519 --> 00:21:49,866
<Default><b>[ATLA] That was an
incredible scream she let out.</b></Default>

423
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:52,410
<Default><b>The Spear Hero sure
is a weird guy, isn't he?</b></Default>

424
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:53,940
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

425
00:21:54,190 --> 00:21:56,359
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

